snippet.title: Splatoon 2 Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Ink-splatting action is back and fresher than ever in Splatoon 2. And this time, take Turf War battles on-the-go with Nintendo Switch. 

Splatoon 2 is Available Now! https://goo.gl/TC3Fvs

#NintendoSwitch #Splatoon2

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot
